{"tid":1353801,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[再開過] 一定要追究八鄉指揮官李漢民同警隊二哥鄧炳強","createTime":"2019-07-23T04:31:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T13:38:49.000Z","uid":108589,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3736f66b2ba7bd5a211826b6096fe0dd9d4244ed","tid":1353801,"uid":108589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:31:56.000Z","msg":"牛屎佬都係古惑仔，係收錢做野。但係無警隊包庇，佢地係唔會咁猖狂。<br />\n星期日一定要警方，特別係八鄉指揮官李漢民，公開解釋點解咁遲先出動，同埋李漢民被拍到同白衣襲擊者講你既好意我心領，係咩意思？李漢民作為警方代表同白衣人有咩關係？<br />\n係全個警察部門故意偏袒黑社會襲擊市民，定係一少撮警務人員同黑社會私底下有勾結？警方有責任向市民公開解釋。<br />\n<br />\n重申訴求：<br />\n立即釋放所有和平示威既被捕人士<br />\n成立獨立調查委員會，調查濫權濫暴警察，以及李漢民以致整個元朗警局有無人私底下同黑社會勾結，故意襲擊返屋企既市民<br />\n<br />\n我地要 Name and Shame 警隊入面既害群之馬，八鄉指揮官李漢民李漢民，你唔可以就咁走左去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我唔係要你驚，而係要你出黎公開交代，你同白衣人既關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你係保護白衣人定保護被襲擊，放工返屋企既香港市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fed86e7c280999950cbe26f13805325c989bc78","tid":1353801,"uid":108589,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:32:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%81%BF%E7%AD%94%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E4%BD%95%E6%99%82%E5%88%B0%E5%A0%B4%E1%85%A0%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E5%85%AB%E9%84%89%E5%88%86%E5%8D%80%E6%8C%87%E6%8F%AE%E5%AE%98-%E9%A0%AD%E5%85%88%E5%92%81%E4%BA%82-%E9%BB%9E%E6%9C%89%E6%A9%9F%E6%9C%83%E7%9D%87%E9%8C%B6-%E6%9C%AA%E6%8B%98%E6%8D%95%E4%BB%BB%E4%BD%95%E4%BA%BA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2581%25BF%25E7%25AD%2594%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E4%25BD%2595%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%2588%25B0%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E1%2585%25A0%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%25E5%2585%25AB%25E9%2584%2589%25E5%2588%2586%25E5%258D%2580%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%258F%25AE%25E5%25AE%2598-%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E5%2585%2588%25E5%2592%2581%25E4%25BA%2582-%25E9%25BB%259E%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%259C%2583%25E7%259D%2587%25E9%258C%25B6-%25E6%259C%25AA%25E6%258B%2598%25E6%258D%2595%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E4%25BD%2595%25E4%25BA%25BA%2F&d=3INNoT16QYf2eZrqTwRUigWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=6c426a1f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2581%25BF%25E7%25AD%2594%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E4%25BD%2595%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%2588%25B0%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E1%2585%25A0%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%25E5%2585%25AB%25E9%2584%2589%25E5%2588%2586%25E5%258D%2580%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%258F%25AE%25E5%25AE%2598-%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E5%2585%2588%25E5%2592%2581%25E4%25BA%2582-%25E9%25BB%259E%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%259C%2583%25E7%259D%2587%25E9%258C%25B6-%25E6%259C%25AA%25E6%258B%2598%25E6%258D%2595%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E4%25BD%2595%25E4%25BA%25BA%2F&h=87e19782\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%81%BF%E7%AD%94%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E4%BD%95%E6%99%82%E5%88%B0%E5%A0%B4%E1%85%A0%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E5%85%AB%E9%84%89%E5%88%86%E5%8D%80%E6%8C%87%E6%8F%AE%E5%AE%98-%E9%A0%AD%E5%85%88%E5%92%81%E4%BA%82-%E9%BB%9E%E6%9C%89%E6%A9%9F%E6%9C%83%E7%9D%87%E9%8C%B6-%E6%9C%AA%E6%8B%98%E6%8D%95%E4%BB%BB%E4%BD%95%E4%BA%BA/</a><br />\n<br />\n元朗昨晚有白衣惡煞在元朗西鐵站外群毆記者及市民。市民投訴報警後，遲遲未見警員執法，有港台記者事後向在場警員查問遲遲未見警員到場原因、以及警方到場時間。元朗區八鄉分區指揮官李漢民回應時向記者稱：「遲唔遲呢，我唔知&hellip;我睇唔到錶呀，Sorry呀！」他又承認，據他所知，未就元朗群毆事件，拘捕任何人。<br />\n<br />\n元朗站內群毆事件之後，大批警員在元朗站對開駐守，一名香港電台女記者上前向警員查問，「阿Sir 想問你哋點解咁遲先嚟？」<br />\n<br />\n元朗區八鄉分區指揮官李漢民稱，「遲唔遲呢我唔知，我哋係收到call先嚟嘅。」記者隨即問何時到達，李回應：「我睇唔到錶呀，Sorry呀！妳見唔見到頭先都幾亂下㗎？見到㗎可？如果見到你就知啦，我哋點會有機會可以睇錶呢？」<br />\n<br />\n李漢民承認，據他所知，未有拘捕人。記者又追問，為何沒有拘捕任何人士、以及為何事發時一個警員都沒有。李顯得極不耐煩，「你唔好質問我先啦！」記者稱只是詢問，並非質問。<br />\n<br />\n李一度稱不會回應單一記者問題，記者問是否需要全部傳媒到場才回應，又稱「唔通你叫曬佢哋落嚟，我驚咩？」李又向記者稱，「你咁樣係唔會令到我驚㗎！」"},{"pid":"0266266d88a1fd7f17589e17430fb9d56ac95d0d","tid":1353801,"uid":108589,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:33:25.000Z","msg":"片<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=514093529132702\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D514093529132702&d=3INNoT16QYf2eZrqTwRUigWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=04fc2452\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=514093529132702</a>"},{"pid":"20d1cb779ba6a5ea5e1ad48bd7f9ae1ec8600665","tid":1353801,"uid":108589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:33:52.000Z","msg":"八鄉指揮官李漢民李漢民，你唔可以就咁走左去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我唔係要你驚，而係要你出黎公開交代，你同白衣人既關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你係保護白衣人定保護被襲擊，放工返屋企既香港市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6643cb7fa5adf2b5c7d1cd912db3949903175a10","tid":1353801,"uid":108606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:34:14.000Z","msg":"第日見到黑驚要跟佢地咁叫：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">警謊</span></strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f87a3593fcb88ac941e43906fa78dbbc0d8a1e2c","tid":1353801,"uid":234935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl