:"係討論點對付牛屎佬既同時，我地必須追究元朗警方係 7 月 21 號晚既責任，特別係八鄉指揮官李漢民同前元朗指揮官鄧炳強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n必須公開交待你地同鄉黑既關係，以息民憤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咩係你地既好意，我地心領？係咩意思？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5cc5e97ff278f0fa2efce551a43ffa26165d5a0","tid":1353801,"uid":108589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:39:53.000Z","msg":"推到出熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔可以俾八鄉指揮官李漢民同警隊二哥鄧炳強就咁就逃避左責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd7514f8351454930786490a24711e723b46c621","tid":1353801,"uid":108589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:40:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/355044/%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E9%BB%91%E5%A4%9C-%E7%89%87%E6%AE%B5%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89-%E5%85%AB%E9%84%89%E6%8C%87%E6%8F%AE%E5%AE%98%E6%9D%8E%E6%BC%A2%E6%B0%91%E6%8B%8D%E7%99%BD%E8%A1%AB%E4%BA%BA%E8%86%8A-%E5%94%94%E4%BD%BF%E6%93%94%E5%BF%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F355044%2F%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%25E9%25BB%2591%25E5%25A4%259C-%25E7%2589%2587%25E6%25AE%25B5%25E6%259B%259D%25E5%2585%2589-%25E5%2585%25AB%25E9%2584%2589%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%258F%25AE%25E5%25AE%2598%25E6%259D%258E%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%258B%258D%25E7%2599%25BD%25E8%25A1%25AB%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%2586%258A-%25E5%2594%2594%25E4%25BD%25BF%25E6%2593%2594%25E5%25BF%2583&d=3INNoT16QYf2eZrqTwRUigWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=94a8e50e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/355044/%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E9%BB%91%E5%A4%9C-%E7%89%87%E6%AE%B5%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89-%E5%85%AB%E9%84%89%E6%8C%87%E6%8F%AE%E5%AE%98%E6%9D%8E%E6%BC%A2%E6%B0%91%E6%8B%8D%E7%99%BD%E8%A1%AB%E4%BA%BA%E8%86%8A-%E5%94%94%E4%BD%BF%E6%93%94%E5%BF%83</a><br />\n<br />\n昨晚於元朗發生的連串襲擊，可見到持武器追打市民的是一群身穿白衣的人士。<br />\n<br />\n最新於網上流傳的短片可見，八鄉分區指揮官李漢民帶領二、三十名警員，與一群白衣人談話。當時白衣人情緒激動，以高昂聲線質問警方「而家趕曬（市民）上車未先？佢哋唔走畀我哋趕佢走」，有人更稱「如果我哋再斬就麻X煩」，亦有人指「聚曬喺商場就麻X煩」。<br />\n<br />\n李漢民其後拍一拍其中一人的肩膀，並安撫在場人士，說：「心領嘅，不過我都唔想大家嘅幫忙，令到我哋辛苦」，其後再指「唔使擔心，okay？」。片段未有拍攝到白衣人群有無散去。<br />\n<br />\n李漢民昨晚曾現身，當時有記者提問為何警隊在市民報警逾一小時後方到場，他當時聲稱太忙亂，「睇唔到錶」而未知時間，又指不會回答記者相關的提問。"},{"pid":"8aaf35e61d0f5d3a2ce2ab59d3841cb521717aad","tid":1353801,"uid":108589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:41:31.000Z","msg":"片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XkRBBHP4p9Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DXkRBBHP4p9Q&d=3INNoT16QYf2eZrqTwRUigWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=a759d26d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XkRBBHP4p9Q</a>"},{"pid":"209785d6ff064edc4457c63a4d726b5adf8b8d9e","tid":1353801,"uid":108589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:42:06.000Z","msg":"證據確鑿<br />\n八鄉指揮官李漢民李漢民，你唔可以就咁走左去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我唔係要你驚，而係要你出黎公開交代，你同白衣人既關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你係保護白衣人定保護被襲擊，放工返屋企既香港市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif